credit.credit-words: Music: Thomas Jarman (1776–1861) Text: Isaac Watts, 1696
3. Thou hast redeemed us with Thy blood And set the pris’ners free; Thou mad’st us kings and priests to God, And we shall reign with Thee.
4. To Him who sits upon the throne, The God whom we adore, And to the Lamb that once was slain, Be glory evermore.
